OL,3,CDad admits killing baby son after more
OL,4,Cthan three years of denials
OL,6,FA father has admitted killing his baby
OL,7,Fson after more than three-and-a-half
OL,8,Fyears of denying he was responsible.
OL,10,FPeter Sayle, 32, went on trial accused
OL,11,Fof murdering six-week-old Huxley Sayle
OL,12,Fby deliberately inflicting serious
OL,13,Finjuries at the family home in
OL,14,FPreston, Lancashire, in June 2022.
OL,16,FBut a week after the trial began, on 9
OL,17,FFebruary, Sayle, who denies murder,
OL,18,Fentered a guilty plea to the offence
OL,19,Fof manslaughter at Preston Crown Court.
