OL,3,CDad admits killing baby son after more
OL,4,Cthan three years of denials
OL,6,FBaby Huxley was rushed to hospital in
OL,7,Fthe early hours of 14 June 2022 after
OL,8,Fhis mother, Livinia Sharples, dialled
OL,9,F999 and told the operator that her son
OL,10,Fwas not breathing, the court heard.
OL,12,FA CT head scan at Royal Preston
OL,13,FHospital revealed unexplained bleeding
OL,14,Fin different parts of Huxley's brain
OL,15,Fwhich raised suspicions of a shaking-
OL,16,Ftype injury and he was transferred to
OL,17,Fthe intensive care unit at Royal
OL,18,FManchester Children's Hospital.
