OL,4,Cthan three years of denials
OL,6,FJurors were told the police found
OL,7,Finternet searches such as "baby crying
OL,8,Fmakes me angry dad" and "I'm getting
OL,9,Fso angry when baby won't sleep," on
OL,10,Fdevices seized from the family's home
OL,11,Fin Fulwood.
OL,13,FFollowing the plea, Detective Chief
OL,14,FInspector Andy Fallows, of Lancashire
OL,15,FPolice, said: "I welcome today's
OL,16,Fmanslaughter plea put forward by Peter
OL,17,FSayle.
