OL,3,CDad admits killing baby son after more
OL,4,Cthan three years of denials
OL,6,F"After three-and-a-half years of
OL,7,Fdenials he has finally admitted that
OL,8,Fhe is responsible for assaulting and
OL,9,Fcausing baby Huxley's death.
OL,11,F"While this has been a particularly
OL,12,Fsensitive and challenging case, my
OL,13,Finvestigation team's relentless focus
OL,14,Fhas always been on achieving justice
OL,15,Ffor baby Huxley. Today we have managed
OL,16,Fto achieve that."
OL,18,FSayle will be sentenced on Thursday 12
OL,19,FFebruary.
